Don José Mexican Restaurant is a family-owned restaurant proudly owned and operated by the Arceo family. Since the opening of our first location in East Hanover, NJ in 1998, we have been dedicated to bringing authentic Mexican cuisine to every plate. The success of this initial venture led to the establishment of our additional locations in Sebring, FL, and Netcong, NJ. Whether you visit our beautiful lakefront location in Florida, or go far up north to our Netcong, NJ location, you can expect the same amazing dishes that have made Don José a beloved dining destination.
